create a new basket

Creates a new basket

(TilroyApiKeyXApiKey)
header Parameters

Request Body schema: application/json
optional

Responses

required

process a basket (v1)

Process a basket by sending it to the Prices-and-Promotions-Engine, validating vouchers and creating giftvouchers.

Lines

The response will contain a convertAction on the line.
The Prices-and-Promotions-Engine can update lines (quantity) or add/delete lines (in case lines of a split eg 2+1).

Sku

For sku we expect the full data for the sku:
  • sourceId
  • brand
  • season
  • productGroup
  • gender
  • tags (not in use)
In case of a product unknown in Tilroy sourceId can be provided, but it will not be taken into account.

Promotions

On line level the reference to the promotion is provided.

Loyalty

Loyalty for this basket expressed in both value and points.

Vouchers

Contains all vouchers added by the customer.
Source system provides the code and Tilroy will respond with:

• type
• valid
• amountOpen: amount open on this voucher
• error: error messages for this voucher

Possible values for type:

• advance
• discount
• unique
• loyalty
• giftvoucher
• creditvoucher

Possible error values:

• CompletelyUsed: no amount open on the voucher
• NotSold: voucher is known but is not active yet
• Cancelled
• NotActiveYet
• Expired

Gift voucher

Source system will provide the amount and Tilroy will respond with:

• reference
• webcode

Once Tilroy assigned reference and webcode in next basket JSON’s we expect the reference and webcode to be filled or Tilroy will generate a new one.

Authorizations:
TilroyApiKey
Request Body schema: application/json
required

The basket JSON in the body of the request

sourceId
required
string

Reference of the basket in the source system

object
languageCode
object

language of the basket (NL, DE, EN, FR)

required
Array of objects (Line)
Array of objects (Voucher)

Vouchers added to the basket by the customer

Array of objects (GiftVoucher)

Sale of gift voucher

required
object
externalLoyalty
required
boolean

Loyalty for this basket is external or not. When a Gezinsbond card is added, for example, externalLoyalty should be true.

externalLoyaltyReference
required
string

Reference for the external loyalty. Basket API will not perform validation in a 3rd party system for this reference.

Responses

https://api.tilroy.com/basketapi2/baskets/process

order-metadata

get delivery services Deprecated

Get all possible delivery services for the given payload.

Payload
You either need to provide enough data for Tilroy to be able to determine the delivery services ('address', 'priceTotal', 'products' & 'shop') or provide the id of an entity where Tilroy can fetch those properties themselves ('orderId', 'quotationId', 'basketId').
For 'sku' and 'shop' either fill in the 'tilroyId' or the 'sourceId' (you could use 'number' for shop as well).

Response
'productDelivery' and '-Service' are nullable, in case when either is not available or implemented.
'price' inside these objects is also nullable for the same reasons.

(TilroyApiKeyXApiKey)

quotationId

Tilroy id of a quotation

basketId

get all delivery dates Deprecated

The service will return all dates in the given 'monthRequested' or in 'dateRange'.
When dateRange property is used, monthRequested is no longer required (and is ignored)

Payload
You either need to provide enough data for Tilroy to be able to determine the delivery services ('address', 'priceTotal', 'products' & 'shop') or provide the id of an entity where Tilroy can fetch those properties themselves ('orderId', 'quotationId', 'basketId').
For 'sku' and 'shop' either fill in the 'tilroyId' or the 'sourceId' (you could use 'number' for shop as well).
In 'deliveryService', 'reference' and 'tilroyId' refer to the same property. TilroyId is deprecated but still supported.

Response
The dates returned are in ISOdate format, but do not regard your locale. They will always be in the 0-time offset ('Z').
'price' is nullable, depending on the implementation.

Authorizations:
(TilroyApiKeyXApiKey)
query Parameters
fields
string

Comma-separated list of all fields you want returned in the result. All other fields will be omitted.

Request Body schema: application/json
required

The payload containing all order data to base the response on.

required
object (AddressCriteria)
object (Language)
required
Array of objects (ProductCriteria)
required
object (Shop)
object
monthRequested
string

must be in format of YYYYMM

object

Responses

https://api.tilroy.com/basketapi2/deliveryservices/getdates
